<arggraph id="micro_c057" topic_id="promote_recycling_by_bottle_deposit" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Protecting our environment is crucial to combating climate change,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[one small change is to promote the recycling of soft drink bottles and cans.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[This is a simple way to reuse plastic and other materials, to decrease the amount of gas that it harvested.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[By developing a small deposit on these cans]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[you encourage people to pick these cans up along the road]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[thus creating a cleaner environment.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[It is also a benefit as it encourages people to go to stores to recycle]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[and then spend that money at the shop increasing the amount spent at the store]]></edu>
  <edu id="e9"><![CDATA[and encouraging economic growth.]]></edu>
